biometric-authentication (0.9.60-0ubuntu1) cosmic; urgency=medium

  * Add Spanish translation
    - Use Google's machine translation to translate relevant text,
      so there is no guarantee of quality for the time being
  * BugFix:
    - Error in content caused by incorrect driver information
    - The interface timeout period is too short, resulting in an
      abnormal interrupt of the interaction process

 -- jianglinxuan (droiing) <jianglinxuan@kylinos.cn>  Thu, 01 Nov 2018 15:51:28 +0800

biometric-authentication (0.9.59-0ubuntu2) cosmic; urgency=medium

  * Enhancement: biometric-auth-client adds API check functionality
  * Optimize the biometric-auth-client interaction
    - The index scope can be omitted when using the search operation
    - Update the manpage of biometric-auth-client
  * Modify compiler dependencies
    - Biometric identification framework services do not require higher
      versions of GTK3.
    - Tested version 3.18 of GTK3 can meet the requirements
  * Update project translation
    - Add the translation for the biometric-auth-client
    - Fix Chinese translation errors
    - Add French, Portuguese and Russian translations
      * Use Google's machine translation to translate relevant text,
        so there is no guarantee of quality for the time being
    - Remove unwanted translations

 -- jianglinxuan (droiing) <jianglinxuan@kylinos.cn>  Tue, 16 Oct 2018 09:06:22 +0800

